race.description: Pizza Holic Eden Country Boosted Handicap
race.comment: RASLOC (10) deep into her prep now and the winkers come off. Came out quickly from the awkward draw when a fading seventh over 1460m at Queanbeyan. Can stalk the speed and score a well-deserved win in this suitable contest. BOMBELLEISTIC (1) resumes with a good fresh record from the low gate. Up in grade when a plugging third over 1600m at Nowra in the soft (7) going. Back without a trial and leading rider booked. COSMIC RIDE (6) has a solid set of figures, and a win looks imminent. Shouldered the 61.5kg when a fading fourth over 1460m at Queanbeyan. Genuine top three player. MAGIC SHOT (2) not that far away at his last two runs and no excuses today fourth up. Kept finding with the 61kg when fourth over this trip at Nowra. Each way prospect.
